Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.55,0:01:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了！不好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.95,0:01:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邮差先生！不好了！所有人都变成动物了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.69,0:01:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 动物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.66,0:01:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 收信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.96,0:01:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是那样啦～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.53,0:01:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好聪明的狗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.10,0:01:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.03,0:01:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的！连你们都变身了 这下子怎么找藉口都没用了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先变身的人是你吧 大笨猫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.51,0:01:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨猫？你再说一次看看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.81,0:01:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大‧笨‧猫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.08,0:01:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.55,0:01:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,够了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.48,0:02:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还、还会说话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.88,0:02:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.25,0:02:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与其拙劣的隐瞒不如干脆说实话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.79,0:02:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 其实我是被狗、由希是被老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.93,0:02:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至于他 草摩夹是被猫的怪物附身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.87,0:02:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪物…吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 草摩家的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.60,0:02:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,几百年来都被和十二生肖相同的怪物附身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.61,0:02:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 猫可以说是例外中的例外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.95,0:02:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要身体虚弱的时候或被异性抱住的话就会变身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.29,0:02:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过一阵子就会自己恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.82,0:02:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.89,0:02:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会变成全裸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.73,0:02:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 让你看到这个丑态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.70,0:02:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我也见识到许多的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被十二生肖的怪物附身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了一个天大的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩就是不想让人知道这个秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.05,0:03:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才会把那个抱住他的二年级学姊推开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.05,0:03:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你说过你想属猫是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？啊 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看过实际的人之后呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.33,0:03:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说得也是 他是猫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过阿夹真是个大笨猫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.43,0:03:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学武之人居然那么容易就被人从背后抓住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.07,0:03:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是天大的耻辱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少也要发现有人在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.17,0:03:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情演变到这个地步 我看你怎么担这个责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.95,0:03:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你哦 真的是眼中只有由希而已…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.35,0:03:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少在那边说那种奇怪的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.85,0:03:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是没注意 那有什么办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.09,0:03:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁晓得这个房子里会有这家伙 会有这个女人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.82,0:03:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.16,0:03:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个房子里有没有女人跟你一点关系都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你是个“局外人”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.66,0:03:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少 少啰唆～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.34,0:04:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 血！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.67,0:04:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？血？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.38,0:04:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早就知道你是个白痴了 没想到蠢到这个地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.35,0:04:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲着你那份傻劲 今天就认真跟你玩玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别让我感到无趣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等着瞧！你这个娘娘腔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.62,0:04:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.46,0:04:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那两个家伙关系超级恶劣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次碰面就只会打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.96,0:04:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可、可是 不阻止他们的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系啦 马上就会分出高下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.48,0:04:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是告诉过你别让我觉得无趣吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.32,0:04:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打…打飞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 控制一点 别把房子打坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到他会飞那么高 根本没有在防御嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本田同学 你的伤势如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.16,0:05:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我、我完全没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.56,0:05:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…那个人呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该不会有事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.67,0:05:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 看到夹 你的猫年梦想应该幻灭了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有新发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.22,0:05:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被称为王子的人居然这么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然早知道他是运动全才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是又有点不太一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和在学校截然不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.87,0:05:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学校！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.10,0:05:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迟到了啦～～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.60,0:05:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要上学 制服上都是泥巴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 昨天才刚挖出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.21,0:05:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 说我跌倒就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.11,0:05:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想可能瞒不过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.75,0:05:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我一定要上学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.02,0:06:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是和过世的妈妈约好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.06,0:06:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过必须先向慊人先生报告这件事才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩家的大当家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.57,0:06:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大当家…吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很了不起的人罗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.37,0:06:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他知道草摩家最大的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.78,0:06:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 好了 我走了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.35,0:06:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看她会到处宣传我们的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.72,0:06:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算消除本田同学的记忆吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.49,0:06:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像以前一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.73,0:06:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我当时也不想那么做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.83,0:06:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是为了避免太多人知道 那也是没办法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 幸好能借到洗衣机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.82,0:07:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也太扯了吧 怎么摔得可以摔成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,L·O·V·E
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.29,0:07:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,LOVELY 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.87,0:07:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦 本田同学 你洗掉啦？全身泥巴比较适合你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王子今天也迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.31,0:07:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些王子亲卫队闷坏了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.62,0:07:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是她们知道我住在草摩家的话一定会担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不能告诉她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我到更衣室去换衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本田同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.97,0:07:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.50,0:07:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没有把我们的事跟朋友说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.11,0:08:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是你不放心的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不会说出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.35,0:08:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈经常说 对别人说长道短的人是坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.72,0:08:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不是这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以发誓 就算要我写血书或是赌命都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈以前也经常这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.53,0:08:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.13,0:08:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然你拼命想保守秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.10,0:08:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是或许还是要消除你的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽说是消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.41,0:08:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过就像是催眠一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.78,0:08:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前也曾经发生过类似的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.66,0:08:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我七岁时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.39,0:08:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在本家的庭园中游玩的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.74,0:09:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果在场的小朋友全部都被消除记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人 我很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.78,0:09:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那么拼命的隐瞒是因为我很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.83,0:09:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人会变身为老鼠当然是件奇怪的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.26,0:09:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是被一般人知道这件事的话 一定会觉得很不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们就会远离你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.44,0:09:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.55,0:09:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.72,0:09:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…对于慊人决定的事 我从来就不敢拂逆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.62,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是什么样的决定都无法反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.84,0:10:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.41,0:10:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的…我真的不是故意的～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.51,0:10:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是大笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.04,0:10:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果没有人看到的话就没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.88,0:10:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.45,0:10:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你为我担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.72,0:10:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.03,0:10:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.86,0:10:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然我知道的是必须通知大当家的重大秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要这么做也是没有办法的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.50,0:10:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就选择最能够让你们放心的方法来处理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.18,0:10:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然要我忘掉这些事感觉有些凄凉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.85,0:10:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 你们肯无条件的把住在帐篷里的我接回来住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.92,0:10:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经十分高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.65,0:11:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我会忍耐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.12,0:11:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算把我的记忆消除了 我们还是朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.73,0:11:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 恢复原状的时间很不规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没…没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.81,0:11:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学 你的领带歪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？唉呀 我对这种事最不擅长了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.48,0:11:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真让人意想不到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在是我表现的机会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是被一般人知道这件事的话 一定会觉得很不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.56,0:11:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们就会远离你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本田同学不会觉得不舒服吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.17,0:11:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托你的福 我的精神百倍！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.24,0:11:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我不是指这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.84,0:11:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天 一起回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.91,0:11:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.99,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们还是朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.76,0:12:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.13,0:12:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别这么说 我本来就很擅长打领带嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.25,0:12:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个小透可以信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.02,0:12:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对由希、阿夹、我 或许这是个好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴？出去了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.35,0:13:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先去放书包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.38,0:13:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.99,0:13:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.83,0:13:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是在做应急处置啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以后再叫专家来重弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在只要能遮雨就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是、是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.10,0:13:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易能和猫相遇却被他讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.88,0:13:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.21,0:13:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我 没能够注意到周遭的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的修行不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才会输给可恶的由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.36,0:13:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天早上…今天早上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉…\N我回来罗～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希、小透 我回来罗～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有既笨又迟钝打架老是输的阿夹～～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么啦 可恶的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那个…猫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.88,0:14:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上就会回来的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.31,0:14:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他没有别的地方去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 小透 你来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.88,0:14:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊、好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我刚刚到慊人那里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.43,0:14:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说要是你能守住秘密的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是可以跟我们一起住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.13,0:14:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不用接受惩罚吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惩罚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要严守秘密就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.98,0:14:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.81,0:14:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 不用被消除记忆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.89,0:14:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.26,0:15:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未免太顺利了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.33,0:15:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人到底有什么盘算？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.57,0:15:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是先相信慊人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得他突然转性了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.28,0:15:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在才说有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.85,0:15:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过还是请你们多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以后多多照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.89,0:15:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 嗯…我们才要你多多照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.89,0:15:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多多指教哦 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.59,0:15:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.63,0:15:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈 几经波折 我终于住进草摩家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来才是艰苦奋战的开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我该做什么好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.77,0:16:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希是那种连折个纸鹤都折不好的笨手笨脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只会碍手碍脚而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.54,0:16:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里交给我就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.64,0:16:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要帮忙做家事就能够免费住进来 对我已经太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.64,0:16:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像这种时候就让我表现吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.71,0:16:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就麻烦你罗 我要出去找阿夹 把他抓回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中午就回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.75,0:16:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 尽管去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.12,0:16:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我也出去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的 包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话虽这么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本田透 加油罗！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.15,0:16:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于结束了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.95,0:17:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了 化腐朽的厨房为神奇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这房子里还有电子锅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我挖出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.39,0:17:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早餐 应该说是午餐了 已经作好罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.10,0:17:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.90,0:17:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗？味道会不会太淡了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.74,0:17:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.04,0:17:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久没有吃到这样的饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.48,0:17:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.54,0:17:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴和蠢猫到底去哪里了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.71,0:17:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说中午就会回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.68,0:17:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别理他们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.02,0:17:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则难得的饭菜都冷掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.26,0:17:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太不可思议了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.83,0:17:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到我能够和草摩同学面对面一起吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.26,0:17:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问 你刚刚也出门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是去买东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.70,0:17:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到后院的秘密基地去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？秘密基地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密基地！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听起来就好兴奋哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.55,0:18:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许和你想像得不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.05,0:18:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次招待你去看看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！可以吗？好高兴哦！秘密基地！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.99,0:18:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小时候我家附近也有一个 可是他们说女生不能进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 好期待哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 你听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.20,0:18:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少啰唆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.86,0:18:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把人玩弄于股掌之间 这样很好玩吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.23,0:18:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别急嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.17,0:18:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是好玩不好玩的问题 全都是为了你好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且这也是慊人决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.01,0:18:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少啰唆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.91,0:18:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是慊人决定的又怎样！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊、欢迎回来 要用午餐吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不需要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何必这样对小透呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有 要从正门进来嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.42,0:18:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鞋子也要脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴 你说这些没有说服力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.55,0:18:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还是第一次看你穿西装呢 好适合哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗!? 真的吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.86,0:18:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像牛郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说午饭做好了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.46,0:18:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 阿夹呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在生气 别理他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天骗他参加编入考试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,编入考试？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.64,0:19:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.44,0:19:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹接下来要和你们念同一所高中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.41,0:19:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要一起住在这个家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准吃！不准过来！滚出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.18,0:19:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然…我就知道你会生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.79,0:19:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹这四个月来下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道他去哪里了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到山上修行去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.37,0:19:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.57,0:19:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是被瀑布淋、和熊决斗的那种修行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.97,0:19:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是吧 阿夹真的很想打败你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.32,0:19:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹会这么想赢 还是为了十二生肖那个故事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.43,0:20:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为猫被老鼠骗了 所以才会怀恨在心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.63,0:20:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 如果问阿夹这些事的话 对他不太好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.41,0:20:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪里？在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.15,0:20:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 就是那边那个橘子头！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.19,0:20:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的是草摩的堂弟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.26,0:20:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和草摩感情好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.39,0:20:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 他在害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.07,0:20:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.97,0:20:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.87,0:20:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感觉到他和草摩由希有相同的电波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.54,0:20:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.74,0:20:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么感应？和“人”的电波不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.14,0:20:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说太失礼了吧～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊、等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是你的堂弟吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然是我堂弟 但是我们不太亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.12,0:21:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也从来不交谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 你要去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！ 等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.43,0:21:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛、好痛～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.73,0:21:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩 怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放开我～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要紧张嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.50,0:21:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要来烦我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.41,0:21:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.41,0:21:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好、好厉害！草摩的堂弟就是不一样！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.41,0:21:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是这里是二楼耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.75,0:21:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛 人家可是女孩子耶 太过分了——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.68,0:21:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般人怎么会跳下去啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是猫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.63,0:21:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.66,0:21:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈 夹果然是猫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.27,0:21:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总有一天我会和他变成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.41,0:21:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好朋友的

